Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.36,0:00:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,New Space Century: The year 3113
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.46,0:00:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Mankind has left the solar system
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.33,0:00:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,in search of life-sustaining habitats.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.27,0:00:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thirty centuries have passed\Nsince the planet
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.50,0:00:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Earth was consumed by toxic pollutants.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.93,0:00:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,At that time, mankind commenced a
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.74,0:00:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,desperate search for habitable planets.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.48,0:00:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A few planets were quickly found\Nand the exodus from Earth began.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.65,0:00:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The ensuing mass exodus from Earth\Nresulted in
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.29,0:00:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,the creation of\Na new interplanetary government;
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.92,0:00:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and it was decreed\Nthat all new planets and space
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.56,0:00:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,colonies would fall\Nunder the jurisdiction
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.93,0:00:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,of The Allied Earth Government,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.46,0:00:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the Domestic Union of Arms (DUA).
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.33,0:00:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,In outer space, to this day,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.60,0:00:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,divisions of the DUA\Ncontinue to comb the cosmos
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.11,0:00:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,for new planets,\Nfor untapped natural resources, and
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.44,0:00:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,for lands fit for habitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.21,0:01:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Of uncharted planets\Ninvolves grave danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.42,0:01:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,To this end,\NDUA has no choice but to depend
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.35,0:01:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,on professional explorers\Ncalled Advancers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.12,0:01:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Advancers,\Nthe chosen ones who boldly land
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.63,0:01:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,on unexplored planets\Nwithout concern for their
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.86,0:01:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,individual safety and lives,\Npartake in the most
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.23,0:01:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,unmerciful of missions:\NFully exposed human
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.63,0:01:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,sacrifices\Nfurthering the cause of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.03,0:01:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, however,\Nthe once elite Advancer corps
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.34,0:01:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,include former treasure hunters\Nand drifters with
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.78,0:01:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,unknown pasts among its honored ranks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.35,0:01:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Mugal, DUA,\NDevelopment Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.10,0:01:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Vanessa Gronne, Warden of M-99,\NWomen's special prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.18,0:01:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,When was Tina Owen sent to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.65,0:01:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,6 months, 13 days ago,\NEarth Standard Time, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.91,0:01:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell her I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.24,0:02:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But Tina is serving\Na 2000 year sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.65,0:02:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.78,0:02:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What a surprise.\NShe is jailed so nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.44,0:02:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,"Long time, Tina."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.02,0:02:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember inviting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.02,0:02:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so cold.\NI've come to set you free.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.92,0:02:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, it was I who first asked you\Nto take that job;
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.08,0:02:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,though you did exceed your authority\Nby destroying that foul planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.32,0:02:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,For the record,\Nit was difficult even for me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.11,0:02:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,to get your sentence lowered\Nto 2000 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.14,0:02:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not interested in your excuses,\Nnor intention of giving you mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.30,0:02:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel responsible for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.39,0:03:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! I know what's on your mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.33,0:03:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,As always, you merely seek\Nto promote your own self interests by
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.23,0:03:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,taking advantage of those\Nwho have no control over their lives;
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.29,0:03:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,like me, rotting in this hell-hole\Nserving a 2000 year sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.70,0:03:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pretty sharp.\NAnyway, this new planet is so horrible
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.71,0:03:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that even the bravest Advancers\Nare afraid of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.70,0:03:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Tina, I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.21,0:03:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.86,0:03:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If you find a habitable zone,\NI'll see that your sentence is voided.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.80,0:03:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll do it? I've brought you\Neverything you'll need.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.88,0:03:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And I will procure\Nanything you request.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.08,0:03:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me take a shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.14,0:03:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...a shower?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.66,0:03:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Not an air shower either!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.25,0:03:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to be a hot water shower,\NEarth-style!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.25,0:03:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...\Nbut that's a luxury in outer space.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.78,0:03:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This prison doesn't even have\Nsuch facilities...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.15,0:03:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can enjoy one in my cruiser.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.45,0:03:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't peek.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.14,0:03:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.77,0:03:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no intention of getting\Nchewed out by you, at least not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.12,0:04:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,R
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.22,0:04:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ri
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.32,0:04:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Rip
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.42,0:04:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ripp
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.52,0:04:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Rippe
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.62,0:04:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ripped
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.72,0:04:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ripped B
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.82,0:04:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ripped By
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.92,0:04:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ripped By H
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.02,0:04:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ripped By Ha
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.12,0:04:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ripped By Han
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.22,0:04:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ripped By Hana
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.32,0:04:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ripped By Hanak
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.42,0:04:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ripped By Hanako
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.33,0:04:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You look incredible, Tina.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.57,0:04:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I am more concerned about\Nthe types of men you are going
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.01,0:04:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,to attract than the actual danger\Nsurrounding your mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.61,0:04:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What if I were to run away right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.35,0:04:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you won't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.32,0:05:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd never be at peace\Non the run with a 2000 year
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.22,0:05:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,sentence hanging over your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.29,0:05:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I've studied all your data\Non the planet, Omega-13.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.12,0:05:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The survival rate is a paltry 1.75%.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe that's enough for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.63,0:05:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you overestimating me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.67,0:05:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.97,0:05:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Space station M-75.\NLevel D.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.84,0:05:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Due to the many transients\Nwho take residence here,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.24,0:05:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,it is rated as\Nthe most lawless station in the galaxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.24,0:06:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Also the largest black market\Nin the galaxy can be found here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.20,0:06:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, sweetheart,\Nwhat are you looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.54,0:06:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a great dick.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.62,0:06:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's have some fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.65,0:06:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got an awesome body!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.66,0:06:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mess with me...\NI'll carve your eyes out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.27,0:06:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.00,0:06:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna kill you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.21,0:07:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.69,0:07:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What is a nice girl like you doing\Nin a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.36,0:07:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a hike.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.63,0:07:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,At least you've got spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.73,0:07:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably more than those outlaws.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.56,0:07:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the black market?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.46,0:07:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmmm, are you intending\Nto go shopping there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.67,0:07:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll find it myself\Nif you won't tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.41,0:07:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.51,0:07:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,A ship. One that is suitable\Nfor treasure hunting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.84,0:07:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,With as many features as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.95,0:07:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me to escort you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.82,0:07:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,3.6 million bol?\NThis used to be an Advancer,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.33,0:07:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Ho's favorite ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.10,0:08:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, it is not the type of item\None can usually purchase,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.43,0:08:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,unless Ho is retiring, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.01,0:08:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,4 million bol!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.01,0:08:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent, Garuda!\NYou truly have a discerning eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.98,0:08:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you planning to go\Non another gold hunt?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.02,0:08:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking for a planet\Nwhere I can escape from women!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.72,0:08:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Don Juan Garuda must finally\Nbe in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.06,0:08:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want, this ship can even take you\Nall the way to hell: Omega-13!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.00,0:08:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,4.5 million bol!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.90,0:08:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.97,0:08:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,4.5 million bol!\NYou've got guts young lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.94,0:08:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,4.5 million, anyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.65,0:08:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,5 million bol!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.95,0:08:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,5.5 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.08,0:08:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit! 5.6 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.05,0:08:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,6 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.89,0:08:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What the fuck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.76,0:09:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.76,0:09:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,6 million! Sold!\NCaptain Ho's ship, "Spider,"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.80,0:09:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,is now hers! But do you really\Nhave that kind of money?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.80,0:09:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Check with the bank at port of entry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.84,0:09:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Tina Owen, and I just got 6 million bol\Nin exchange for the newest DUA ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.48,0:09:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.\NCome and sign the required documents.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.45,0:09:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're very lucky. Rarely can one\Nobtain a prized-ship like Captain Ho's.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.69,0:09:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of it, you out-bid Garuda;\Na man with a most discerning eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.40,0:09:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Tina... Owen...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.35,0:09:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.38,0:10:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,L-I'm not a thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.55,0:10:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, weren't you just trying\Nto steal this? Weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.46,0:10:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I was hoping to carry it for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.33,0:10:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have a place\Nto stay on this station, yet, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.13,0:10:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take you there!\NPlease, let me do things for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.93,0:10:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm much more useful than you think!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.10,0:10:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What about your family?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.70,0:10:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,L-I'm alone.\NI'm a space refugee, an orphan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.11,0:10:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't feel sorry for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.34,0:10:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doing quite fine on my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.88,0:10:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.85,0:10:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Really!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.08,0:10:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm starving.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.49,0:10:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I know a good place!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.39,0:10:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.56,0:10:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Frill.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.66,0:10:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Frill, you don't have to pretend\Nto be a boy in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.23,0:10:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You are a girl, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.66,0:10:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You knew that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.10,0:10:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.30,0:10:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Tina, Tina Owen!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.44,0:10:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.67,0:10:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! You were so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.21,0:10:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And on top of it,\Nyou're extraordinarily beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.12,0:11:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to compete with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.66,0:11:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Garuda!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.29,0:11:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the kind of chick you rarely see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.40,0:11:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave Tina alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.23,0:11:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not the kind of woman\Nthat you flirt with!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.17,0:11:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.24,0:11:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you to her, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.04,0:11:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.89,0:11:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but this is the only place\Nthat's open.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.72,0:11:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But the food here is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.19,0:11:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to you,\NI was able to get a room with a door.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.83,0:11:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so surprising:
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.16,0:11:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're telling me that most hotel rooms\Non this station don't have doors?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.14,0:11:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.00,0:12:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,"A long time ago, when supply ships\Nwere unable to reach this"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.54,0:12:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,station and its heating system\Nbroke-down, the station's residents were
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.01,0:12:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,forced to get their heat from everything\Nand anything they could burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.14,0:12:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Frill,\Ndo you want to stay here with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.45,0:12:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.22,0:12:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any other place to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.49,0:12:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the space ship\NI just purchased at auction is ready,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.72,0:12:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,there are a number of things\NI need you to get for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.56,0:12:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do anything for you, Tina.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.16,0:12:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But, then... you are going to dump me\Nafter that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.06,0:12:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to a place\Nwhere I can't take you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.50,0:12:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Tina, you belong to a better world.\NI can tell."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.51,0:12:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.51,0:12:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to a place where survival\Nis far from guaranteed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.35,0:12:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I can't take you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.18,0:12:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Tina?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.95,0:12:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,After you finish your meal,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.35,0:12:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,go and gather as much information\Nas possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.79,0:12:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,about the planet Omega-13.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.92,0:12:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But that planet is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.39,0:12:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.83,0:12:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you're an Advancer!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.79,0:12:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. And if I survive,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.23,0:13:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I will come back here\Nso that we can see each other again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.43,0:13:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you hire me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.47,0:13:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Akira Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.04,0:13:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you been following me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.17,0:13:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have malicious intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.34,0:13:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth,\Nthis is the very area where
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.48,0:13:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,all my money\Nand my ship's key were stolen...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.08,0:13:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,from a hotel room without a door.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.15,0:13:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.55,0:13:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't take action now,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.95,0:13:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I am probably going to die\Nin some ditch on this station.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.66,0:13:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I've worked on Advancer crews\Ntwice previously;
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.16,0:13:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,though both times,\Nthe missions failed...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.29,0:13:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I have been waiting here\Nfor another job as an Advancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.73,0:13:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you know about Omega-13?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.43,0:13:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I know a lot more\Nthan that little twerp!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.37,0:13:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Screw you!\NI've got sharp ears!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.61,0:13:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll decide\Non whether to hire you or not
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.98,0:13:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,after hearing more\Nof what you've got to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.64,0:13:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Frill, can you get the medical supplies
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.05,0:13:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and the parts I've written down here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.08,0:13:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And also,\Npurchase whatever information you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.82,0:13:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No sweat!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.23,0:14:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better let me do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.50,0:14:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, you'll feel good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.13,0:14:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.54,0:14:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We are in God's service!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.20,0:14:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Even God will be pleased\Nwhen you do it with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.81,0:14:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So stop struggling!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.48,0:14:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.68,0:14:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoops... They're fake nuns!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.92,0:14:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,She's got a really shapely ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.66,0:14:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.36,0:14:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.97,0:14:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This will be\Nabsolutely unforgettable for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.62,0:15:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Someone! H-Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.92,0:15:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.06,0:15:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the fuck are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.94,0:15:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Garuda?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.98,0:15:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Joanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.96,0:15:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You maggots...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.36,0:15:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Garuda, I missed you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.76,0:15:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! What were you thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.43,0:15:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,trailing after me disguised as a nun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.23,0:15:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Garuda, I'm not going to leave you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.14,0:15:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.01,0:15:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You will leave here, tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.08,0:15:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a job to do, understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.78,0:15:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I owe you one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.58,0:16:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to thank me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.51,0:16:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Your luck has run out, Garuda.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.78,0:16:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut the fuck up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.46,0:16:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So far, seven Advancer parties\Nhave left for Omega-13.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.09,0:16:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But none have returned yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.33,0:16:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Nine parties, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.73,0:16:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Two other parties were unofficial:\NTreasure hunters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.40,0:16:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Frill's sharp ears\Naren't so bad after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.50,0:16:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,See. I told you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.41,0:16:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That explains why there's no data
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.91,0:16:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,available detailing Omega-13's surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.68,0:16:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that treasure hunters have set
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,there sights there\Nindicates that it must
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.48,0:16:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,have some valuable natural resources,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.38,0:16:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,even if the planet is uninhabitable!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.55,0:16:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true. However, according to
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.02,0:16:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,surveillance data from our satellite,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.89,0:16:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,87% of the planet's surface falls\Nwithin the "high temperature" zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.76,0:16:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It could be like a scorched desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.93,0:16:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Worse, even if there is oxygen,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.43,0:16:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,there could also be noxious pollutants.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.23,0:16:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to quit,\Nyou should do it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.34,0:16:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If I quit now, you'll be unemployed\Neffective immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.87,0:17:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that acceptable?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.17,0:17:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I going do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.81,0:17:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no desire to view your corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.51,0:17:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira is a chicken!\NI'm going with you, Tina!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.41,0:17:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.12,0:17:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Say it's okay, Tina!\NI have nowhere else to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.32,0:17:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take me with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.92,0:17:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you afraid of dying?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.62,0:17:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing compares to the loneliness\Nof being all-alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.53,0:17:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.33,0:17:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Tina!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.43,0:17:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.33,0:17:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I just didn't want to let you go if
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.77,0:17:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I could possibly stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.54,0:17:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira, haven't you been waiting for
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.37,0:17:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,an opportunity to go to Omega-13,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.51,0:17:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,from the very beginning?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.17,0:17:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.04,0:17:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your real intention?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.31,0:17:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The same as Garuda's!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.28,0:17:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He just wants to strike-it-rich!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.01,0:17:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not right!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.02,0:17:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm after the man who killed my parents\Nand my sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.42,0:17:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I know\Nthat he passed through this station.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.33,0:17:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ortega is his name;\Na fallen Advancer,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.26,0:17:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,who is now a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.43,0:17:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You think he's on Omega-13?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.40,0:18:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If he's still alive.\NOnce he strikes gold, however,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.53,0:18:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure\Nhe'll pass back through this station.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.70,0:18:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It is for that day,\Nthat I have remained here, waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.14,0:18:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you sleep on it\Nuntil tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.17,0:18:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not really compelled to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.17,0:18:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Tina, why do you so emphatically adhere\Nto Omega-13?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.81,0:18:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,As an Advancer,\Nyou should be able to
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.45,0:18:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,choose a planet\Nwith a much higher survival rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.95,0:18:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a deal I have made\Nfor the commutation
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.25,0:18:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,of a 2000 year prison sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.85,0:18:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I prefer not to discuss it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.69,0:18:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I'm going with you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.86,0:18:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't just simply watch you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.56,0:18:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night, Tina, Frill.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.03,0:18:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He has a crush on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.03,0:18:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.80,0:18:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He likes you! I can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.44,0:18:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's shows in his eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.87,0:18:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,by the way he looks at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.84,0:18:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Frill, a bit precocious, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.29,0:18:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so good!! Garuda!\NI won't leave you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.89,0:19:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so good!!\NIt's good! It's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.83,0:19:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the Grim Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.43,0:19:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.20,0:19:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll follow you anywhere! Garuda!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.81,0:19:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So-o-o... Garuda!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.78,0:19:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Together, we'll... Ah! G-Garuda!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.19,0:19:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Tina, It's a beautiful planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.92,0:19:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you see what's in my mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.46,0:19:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I am born with supernatural powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.46,0:19:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I can talk to islands,\Nfish, even plants.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.40,0:19:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.30,0:19:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NI can link my heart with yours, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.84,0:19:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the planet\Nyou're originally from?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.17,0:19:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.94,0:19:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But my memory suddenly goes blank\Nat this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.95,0:19:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it by any chance\Nthe legendary planet, Noah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.62,0:20:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.\NNoah is only a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.55,0:20:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No one has ever confirmed\Nits existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.73,0:20:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you see me\Nwhen I was at around your age?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.70,0:20:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.54,0:20:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I only remember that period vaguely,\Nin bits-and-pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.34,0:20:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, clear,\Nconcrete memories don't actually
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.54,0:20:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,start until I was about 14 years old;
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.74,0:20:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,when I was\Nin DUA's Pioneer Training Center...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.28,0:20:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What about your family?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.88,0:20:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know...\NI'm sort of like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.82,0:20:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to see them?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.28,0:20:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NBut if it is the planet Noah which is
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.32,0:20:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,appearing in my memory,\Nit is probably
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.25,0:20:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing more than an illusion I've
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.29,0:20:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,created from some past dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.36,0:20:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Try and remember more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.83,0:20:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday you will learn the truth\Nonce and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.93,0:20:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.00,0:20:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you look cool, Frill!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.64,0:20:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to propose to me,\Nit's now or never!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.07,0:20:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool! You're ten years too early.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.08,0:21:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everything ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.48,0:21:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye-aye, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.98,0:21:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's get moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.98,0:21:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to Omega-13, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.22,0:21:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows? Get in touch with me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.26,0:21:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,if you get in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.69,0:21:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't feel comfortable\N"owing you one."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.13,0:21:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Garuda must have obtained some
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.56,0:21:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,secret data we're not privy to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.63,0:21:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It is better not to trust him too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.20,0:21:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.37,0:21:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He is the type of man who would employ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.41,0:21:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,any means to attain his objectives.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.98,0:21:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.69,0:21:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a gold mine!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.36,0:21:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Joanna, you ladies stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.00,0:22:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Is anyone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.98,0:22:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Garuda! Garuda! Help!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.82,0:22:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Joanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.22,0:22:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva, what are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.09,0:22:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But Master Garuda told us not to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.23,0:22:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But... Let's get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.66,0:22:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go where Garuda is!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.53,0:23:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Cecil, Eva,\Nif we stay here we'll get killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.67,0:23:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.86,0:23:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Holy shit! Gold everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.53,0:23:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.53,0:23:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Garuda's ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.07,0:23:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's being attacked\Nby an alien creature
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.90,0:23:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,coming out of that drifting ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.84,0:23:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,"This is Tina from Spider."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.41,0:23:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,"Garuda, come back! Garuda!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.38,0:23:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,They must all be\Ninside the drifting ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.66,0:24:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming with you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.56,0:24:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Frill, you stay here!\NIf that creature attacks,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.03,0:24:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,you must flee immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.53,0:24:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, we won't be able\Nto come back either.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.50,0:24:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.57,0:24:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how to operate this,\Ndon't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.17,0:24:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I do! Tina!?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.24,0:24:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.21,0:24:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Tina. Come back soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.73,0:24:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.33,0:24:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,They must be in the transport vessel!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.92,0:25:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Tina!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.74,0:25:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a voice recorder!?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.91,0:25:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.01,0:25:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Joanna, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.42,0:25:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Cecil! Eva!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.55,0:25:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to Master Garuda!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.30,0:25:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No-o-o-o!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.28,0:26:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.84,0:26:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What a sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.59,0:26:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Garuda!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.46,0:26:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Joanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.96,0:26:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva and Cecil...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.50,0:26:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.10,0:26:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no survivors here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.73,0:26:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I located the voice recorder.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.87,0:27:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It will tell us\Nof the last moments on this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.04,0:27:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.71,0:27:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.71,0:27:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... Tina...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.68,0:27:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Tina!!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.42,0:27:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Frill!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.32,0:27:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Tina, hurry!!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.39,0:27:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Garuda, after you!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.59,0:27:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate it!\NWait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.63,0:28:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Tina!?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.56,0:28:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Frill, Joanna is okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.37,0:28:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.30,0:28:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You did well in protecting the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.37,0:28:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We're now going to enter\Nthe atmosphere!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.61,0:28:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The targeted landing point selected by
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.61,0:28:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Tina is within the "mild climate" area!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.41,0:28:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Garuda, play the voice recorder!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.65,0:28:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This is incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.11,0:28:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the gold strike of a lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.38,0:28:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.05,0:28:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't leave me any water,\Nany food!?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.96,0:28:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you intending to monopolize
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.39,0:29:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,the riches of this planet!?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.69,0:29:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Drop dead, Ortega!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.63,0:29:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you son-of-a-bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.10,0:29:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ortega!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.83,0:29:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What's that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.47,0:29:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Nauman! ...What happened!?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.81,0:29:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.18,0:29:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll save my revenge for next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.34,0:29:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as Tina discovers\Na habitable zone,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.61,0:29:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,we should return to the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.55,0:29:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I can come back here by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.68,0:29:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, that's what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.09,0:29:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Garuda! Your purpose
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.29,0:29:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,must be the same as Ortega's!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.99,0:29:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't bring Ortega into this until
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.99,0:29:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Tina finishes her mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.29,0:29:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well first, we have to land safely!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.00,0:29:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know what's gonna\Nhappen next!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.03,0:29:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You mother fucker!!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.10,0:29:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira!\NGaruda is free to go his own
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.60,0:29:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,way after we land!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.47,0:29:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so short-tempered!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.57,0:29:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,She seems far more reasonable than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.04,0:29:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,For the record, I don't want to be
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.31,0:29:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,indebted to her any more, either.\NSo don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.81,0:29:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We're entering the atmosphere now!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.32,0:30:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Frill, let's get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.62,0:30:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye-aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.09,0:30:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, buddy,\Nyou've fallen in love with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.23,0:30:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Temperature: 110 F
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.47,0:30:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Humidity: 20%
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.24,0:30:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No harmful bacteria\Nor toxic pollutants detected.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.21,0:30:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We are way off\Nour targeted landing point.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.31,0:31:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We're lucky to be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.28,0:31:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We can just manage\Nwith the oxygen on this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.78,0:31:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But we should be careful to conserve
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.52,0:31:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,as much oxygen as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.62,0:31:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.19,0:31:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,First, I am going to fix my ship,\N"Boar."
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.92,0:31:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll definitely pay-you-back.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.79,0:31:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You have\Nsuch a strong sense of obligation.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.83,0:31:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Just don't get in our way,\Nthat's all I ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.86,0:31:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,She misjudges me!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.90,0:31:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Tina... I don't know what to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.77,0:31:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But I could not save your friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.04,0:31:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.31,0:31:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.42,0:31:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hot!\NTina, this is like a sauna!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.20,0:32:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira, once we complete\Nour initial investigation,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.04,0:32:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll rest until night time.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.87,0:32:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye-aye, Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.55,0:32:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Frill, once darkness falls\Nit's going to get very cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.72,0:32:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Pace yourself.\NCollect samples of all plants, minerals
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.42,0:32:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and small living things,\Nas you come across them.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.33,0:32:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.53,0:32:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay within sight\Nof the exploring vehicle at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.03,0:32:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we are consuming\Nso much energy in this heat,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.50,0:32:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,we will conclude our work.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.44,0:32:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye-aye, Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.94,0:32:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Tina?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.97,0:32:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.61,0:32:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure is a hot planet,\Nand I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.28,0:32:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,what could have prevented Ortega and
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.64,0:32:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,the other Advancers from returning.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.52,0:32:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually,\NI was thinking the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.02,0:32:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You must not underestimate this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.09,0:32:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Something beyond your worst nightmares
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.52,0:32:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,could suddenly transpire,\Nso be sure to
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.49,0:32:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,never leave yourself exposed!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.99,0:32:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure! You, too, Tina!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.24,0:33:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see even a single plant...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.47,0:33:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But then how is oxygen on this
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.81,0:33:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,planet being generated?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.02,0:33:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Frill!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.65,0:33:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Frill!?\NFrill!!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.19,0:33:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Tina... I...\Ndidn't tell you..., but,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.49,0:33:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm mix blooded:\NHalf human, half Shamoan...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.30,0:33:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,When my body senses\Nsomething abnormal...,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.20,0:33:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,my Shamoan features come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.30,0:33:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And I now feel\Nan enormous number of plants...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.84,0:33:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,On top it,\Nthey are so powerful and violent.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.79,0:33:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira! Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.66,0:34:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Garuda, let's go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.17,0:34:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel the temperature dropping.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.54,0:34:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Not so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.50,0:34:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We came here\Nto do some treasure hunting!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.07,0:34:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.14,0:34:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be a vein of gold!!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.41,0:34:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There, the opening\Nthat is showing on the surface!?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.15,0:34:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Or it might even be Ortega's
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.21,0:34:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and that other guys' excavation site!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.99,0:34:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Garuda!! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.30,0:34:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.63,0:34:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I will just go in and see what's\Nin there. That will be it for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.23,0:34:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If something happens,\Nyou drive the land cruiser.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.67,0:34:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.85,0:35:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this Ortega?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.60,0:35:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Garuda!!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.17,0:35:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Holy shit! We've got to go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.21,0:35:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.69,0:35:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Tina! Hurry into the space ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.53,0:35:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Frill! Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.27,0:35:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.46,0:36:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No-o-o!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.76,0:36:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Frill!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.20,0:37:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Frill! Get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.44,0:37:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ti... Tina?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.47,0:37:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, listen carefully!\NI'll stop them right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.48,0:37:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You go to the back engine room\Nand open the
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.24,0:37:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,emergency cockpit!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.71,0:37:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The ship will execute\Nan emergency lift-off!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.02,0:37:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We will tear ourselves away from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.29,0:37:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.52,0:37:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira! Akira! Are you alive!?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.33,0:37:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.26,0:38:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all okay, Tina?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.60,0:38:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Garuda! S-Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.55,0:38:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Joanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.28,0:38:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Holy S-Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.26,0:38:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Tina, please take care of Joanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.73,0:38:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I am... PAYING YOU BACK!!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.70,0:38:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Garuda!!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.84,0:38:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Joanna!!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.11,0:38:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Joanna!!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.19,0:38:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Tina, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.89,0:39:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Tina! Abandon me and run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.73,0:39:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.51,0:39:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira, open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.34,0:39:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew, we've made it...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.98,0:39:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What a horrible planet!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.42,0:40:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Tina,\Nthere's something wrong with Joanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.46,0:40:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Take the helm of the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.63,0:40:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Put some clothes on.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.63,0:40:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,My self-control cannot withstand\Nmuch more of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.34,0:40:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No-o-o-o!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.88,0:40:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Frill, go to Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.78,0:40:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.78,0:40:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Go now!!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.08,0:40:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.29,0:40:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you like\Nthe greatest force in the cosmos?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.90,0:40:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on,\NI will rule the entire cosmos!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.51,0:41:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll devour all pleasures\Nthat exist in space!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.95,0:41:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No-o-o-o!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.12,0:41:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Tina!!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.12,0:41:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ortega!?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.26,0:41:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be my nutritional ecstasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.36,0:41:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.93,0:41:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot!! Don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.27,0:42:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Tina,\NI've forwarded your report regarding
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.31,0:42:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,planet Omega-13 to HQ.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.51,0:42:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Once HQ verifies your report,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.48,0:42:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,your sentence will be reduced\Nto 1000 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.61,0:42:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?!\NShe found you a gold-filled planet!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.55,0:42:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You cheapskate!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.89,0:42:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this little one the new crew member
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.62,0:42:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,you were talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.02,0:42:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the one-and-only!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.79,0:42:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't forget about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.06,0:42:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So... what is my next assignment?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.20,0:42:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It is still being discussed.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.83,0:42:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You can relax here for a while.
